 * Gather and analyse market information, monitor the performance of credit
   facilities utilization to identify early signs of credit deterioration;

 * Make recommendations and review on credit risk management strategies to
   comply with relevant regulatory requirements;

 * Perform portfolio analysis to identify potential credit risks and provide
